<title>kẖdny fy ḥḍnk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- kẖdny fy ḥḍnk ṭmny ạ̉smʿ nbḍ ạlḥb fy
 qlby
 ḍmny ạ̉ktr nạḥyẗ qlbk ạ̉nạ mḥtạj lḥḍnk rby
 1- kẖdny fy ḥḍnk kẖlyny ạ̉ʿrf qṣdk fy ḥyạty
 wạlṣwrẗ ạlly fy qlbk ly tẓhr rby fy ṣfạty
 2- kẖdny fy ḥḍnk wạmlạny mn nbʿ ạlḥb ạlṣạfy
 ạ̉rjʿ ạ̉ḥb ạlnạs tạny wạ̉ʿln ḥbk ạlkạfy
 3- kẖdny fy ḥḍnk wạsẖfyny mn kl jrwḥ jwạyạ
 wbjrạḥạtk ạsbyny rby yswʿ dạ ạ̹nt dwạyạ</lyrics>
